keyFacts: The document is a technical label for a Western Digital 500GB hard drive (model WD5003ABYX).
The drive was manufactured in Malaysia and has a date stamp of June 2, 2013.
The document is included in the Epstein case files (EFTA00002513), indicating it is likely evidence related to seized digital storage media.
